Package: flipscores
Version: 1.3.2
Date: 2026-04-17
Title: Robust Score Testing in GLMs, by Sign-Flip Contributions 
Authors@R: 
    c(person("Livio", "Finos", email = "livio.finos@unipd.it", role = c("cre","aut"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-3181-8078")),
    person("Jelle J.", "Goeman", role = "ctb"),
    person("Jesse", "Hemerik", role = "ctb"),
    person("Riccardo","De Santis", role = "ctb"),
    person("Andrea","Panarotto", role = "ctb"))
Description: Provides robust tests for testing in GLMs, by sign-flipping score contributions. The tests are robust against overdispersion, heteroscedasticity and, in some cases, ignored nuisance variables. See Hemerik, Goeman and Finos (2020) <doi:10.1111/rssb.12369> and  De Santis, Goeman, Hemerik, Davenport, Finos (2025) <doi:10.1080/01621459.2025.2491775>.
Imports: MASS, methods
